                        or employee data are compromised.</span></li>
                <li><strong>Enterprise Dashboard:</strong> <span>Monitor and manage security status for all registered
                        company email addresses.</span></li>
                <li><strong>Proactive Security Recommendations:</strong> <span>Receive insights to enhance your
                        company's security practices.</span>
                </li>
                <li><strong>Priority Enterprise Support:</strong> <span>Reach out to our dedicated enterprise team at <a
                            href="mailto:support@newscollector.io">support@newscollector.io</a> for assistance.</span></li>
            </ul>
            <p>Explore our <a href="{{loginLink}}">website</a> to learn more about our features and resources. We're
                thrilled to partner with you in securing your organization's digital assets.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="table-wrapper">
            <!-- Signoff -->
            <div class="pre-text">
                {{!-- {{> signoff}} --}}
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <!-- Footer -->
            {{!-- {{> footer}} --}}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>